p: In the matter of the application of Han Lee for a writ of Habeas Corpus
At chambers before his Honor C Jacobs Judge of District Court holding terms at Seattle in King } Jan 23d 1874

Ah Chaw makes return on writ of of Habeas Corpus to which return Higgins atty for Petitioner as the of said return by supporters to return sustained and Deft Ah Chaw by atty orders obtains to around his return
return filed by atty of Deft Ah Chaw Plff Han Lee files denial of the facts set forth in Defts return
Subscribed Sworn Han Lee Sworn H.S.
Dismissed at cost of Petitioner and Seo Kim Discharged
